    • Method Detail

      • execute

        java.lang.String execute(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                         javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response)
        This method is used to retrieve data from jsp and perform specific commands.
        Parameters:
        request - This is the first parameter to execute method, which helps to get values from the jsp, set the attributes, get the value of the session and redirect.
        response - This is the second parameter to execute method, which used to answer and to transmit data jsp.
        Returns:
        String This returns empty string.
        See Also:
        HttpServletRequest, HttpServletResponse
